cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.DL 

This paper deals with analyzing search trends using web search logs and Wikipedia page views. The most relevant sub-category is Information Retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with search engines and search logs. The paper also involves analyzing data and trends, which falls under Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) and Sound and Music Computing (cs.SD). The paper also involves open data, which falls under Cybersecurity (cs.CY) and Digital Libraries (cs.DL).
